I timed it.

352
00:25:12,464 --> 00:25:15,000
Well, it wasn't me
little donkey's shite, was it?

353
00:25:15,034 --> 00:25:18,003
It was me pony's shite, which
shows how much you were listenin'.

354
00:25:18,037 --> 00:25:20,439
None of it helps me,
do you understand?

355
00:25:20,472 --> 00:25:23,042
None of it helps me.

356
00:25:31,183 --> 00:25:33,885
We'll just chat
about somethin' else then.

357
00:25:43,228 --> 00:25:44,229
(SIGHS)

358
00:25:58,309 --> 00:25:59,577
What's the matter with ya?

359
00:25:59,611 --> 00:26:00,878
Nothin'.

360
00:26:00,912 --> 00:26:02,347
Aren't we going for a sherry?

361
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,848
Don't feel like it.

362
00:26:05,516 --> 00:26:08,853
No, I'm not having this
again today!

363
00:26:13,191 --> 00:26:15,326
Hey! What the hell's going on
with you and me fecking brother?

364
00:26:15,360 --> 00:26:16,961
Don't come in here
shouting the odds at me

365
00:26:16,995 --> 00:26:18,462
