368
00:26:21,665 --> 00:26:23,533
Why can't I?

369
00:26:23,567 --> 00:26:26,670
Why can't ya?
Because it isn't nice.

370
00:26:26,704 --> 00:26:27,739
Do you want a sherry, Siobhan?

371
00:26:27,771 --> 00:26:28,972
No!
Righty-ho.

372
00:26:29,006 --> 00:26:30,474
Has he said somethin' to ya
when he was drunk?

373
00:26:30,507 --> 00:26:31,942
No, I prefer him
when he's drunk.

374
00:26:31,975 --> 00:26:33,910
