I have the problem with.

375
00:26:33,944 --> 00:26:35,747
What's the fecking matter, then?

376
00:26:35,779 --> 00:26:37,214
He's dull, Siobhan.

377
00:26:38,181 --> 00:26:39,182
He's what?

378
00:26:40,350 --> 00:26:41,351
He's dull.

379
00:26:43,954 --> 00:26:47,457
But he's always been dull.
What's changed?

380
00:26:48,325 --> 00:26:49,893
I've changed.

381
00:26:49,926 --> 00:26:53,930
I just don't have a place for
dullness in me life anymore.

382
00:26:55,432 --> 00:26:58,235
But you live on an island
off the coast of Ireland, Colm.

383
00:26:58,268 --> 00:27:01,204
What the hell
are you hoping for, like?

384
00:27:01,238 --> 00:27:03,372
For a bit of peace, Siobhan.
That's all.

385
00:27:04,373 --> 00:27:07,009
For a bit of peace
in me heart, like.

386
00:27:07,910 --> 00:27:11,180
You can understand that.
Can't ya?

387
00:27:20,423 --> 00:27:21,557
Can't ya?

388
