(BELL TOLLING)
(PEACEFUL MUSIC PLAYING)

432
00:29:46,165 --> 00:29:48,134
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

433
00:30:19,531 --> 00:30:23,468
(PEACEFUL MUSIC
CONTINUES PLAYING)

434
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:30,442
What happened to you?

435
00:30:30,475 --> 00:30:32,879
Me daddy discovered
the poteen situation.

436
00:30:32,912 --> 00:30:34,145
SIOBHAN: Oh, Jesus, Dominic!

437
00:30:34,179 --> 00:30:36,081
You poor thing, ya.

438
00:30:36,114 --> 00:30:37,917
