440
00:30:39,317 --> 00:30:41,152
I wouldn'ta minded,
but for the spout.

441
00:30:42,087 --> 00:30:43,188
Do you want a ride to church?

442
00:30:43,221 --> 00:30:44,757
Uh, feck them gobshites!

443
00:30:44,790 --> 00:30:46,056
Dominic!

444
00:30:46,090 --> 00:30:48,827
