impure thoughts about, is it?

472
00:32:41,771 --> 00:32:43,605
Are you joking me?

473
00:32:43,639 --> 00:32:46,541
I mean,
are you fecking joking me?

474
00:32:46,575 --> 00:32:50,079
People do have impure thoughts
about men, too.

475
00:32:50,113 --> 00:32:52,414
Do you have impure thoughts
about men, Father?

476
00:32:53,515 --> 00:32:56,451
I do not have
impure thoughts about men.

477
00:32:56,485 --> 00:32:59,755
