about a man of the cloth?

478
00:32:59,788 --> 00:33:01,489
Well, you started it.

479
00:33:01,522 --> 00:33:04,492
Well, you can get out of my
confessional right now, so you can.

480
00:33:04,525 --> 00:33:06,260
