the meantime then, eh, Father?

483
00:33:09,798 --> 00:33:10,799
I'll be pure fucked!

484
00:33:11,767 --> 00:33:13,035
You will be pure fucked!

485
00:33:13,068 --> 00:33:16,570
Yes, you will be pure fucked!

486
00:33:31,920 --> 00:33:33,387
