494
00:33:48,936 --> 00:33:51,072
I have a set of shears at home.

495
00:33:51,105 --> 00:33:54,075
And each time you bother me
from this day on,

496
00:33:54,108 --> 00:33:55,676
I'll take those shears

497
00:33:55,710 --> 00:33:57,678
and I'll take one
of me fingers off with them.

498
00:33:58,378 --> 00:34:00,147
And I'll give that finger to ya.

499
00:34:00,181 --> 00:34:03,050
A finger from me left hand.
Me fiddle hand.

500
00:34:03,084 --> 00:34:05,218
And each day you bother me more,

501
00:34:05,251 --> 00:34:06,954
